13
00:00:34,490 --> 00:00:38,460
Does that mean they might be together?

14
00:00:38,620 --> 00:00:40,170
Who knows?

15
00:00:40,170 --> 00:00:41,580
Oh? Haha.

16
00:00:42,580 --> 00:00:44,250
Ah, good morning.

17
00:00:44,250 --> 00:00:46,840
Good morning.
I look forward to working with you again.

18
00:00:46,840 --> 00:00:48,010
Likewise, I look forward to working with you.

19
00:00:48,010 --> 00:00:49,300
The dressing room is over there.

20
00:00:49,590 --> 00:00:51,050
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

21
00:00:51,050 --> 00:00:51,970
Good morning.

22
00:00:51,970 --> 00:00:53,050
Oh! You're here!

23
00:00:53,050 --> 00:00:54,260
Good morning.

24
00:00:54,470 --> 00:00:55,470
