25
00:00:56,930 --> 00:00:59,930
Thank you.

26
00:01:02,150 --> 00:01:04,400
If you truly care about him...

27
00:01:05,020 --> 00:01:07,190
And for his future...

28
00:01:08,280 --> 00:01:10,110
You know what I mean, right?

29
00:01:11,070 --> 00:01:13,320
